descriptionHtml:
I made this for myself because I preferer the some of the vanilla menus over SkyUI (mainly crafting) and I decided to upload it here.
This is basically [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29440/?]SkyUI-Away[/url] but with a fomod so it can be easier to use for new people modding their game.

Make sure to disable the warning messages in SkyUI's MCM Menu or download this: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72247/?]SkyUI Warning Remove[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/25680284/?][b]Yexian[/b] [/url]
[color=#e06666]LOAD THIS AFTER SKYUI!!!
[/color]
